prompts.user_prompt_template:
Generate a Leveled Reading Passage:

Level: {LEVEL}
Week: {WEEK}
Topic: {TOPIC}
Word count: {WORD_COUNT}
Target vocabulary: {VOCAB_WORDS}

Provide:
1. title: passage title
2. passage: the reading text (using only level-appropriate vocabulary)
3. word_count: actual count
4. new_words: [{word, meaning_ar, context_in_passage}] — max 5
5. comprehension_questions: 5 questions (3 literal, 2 inference)
6. discussion_prompt: one question for voice lounge discussion
7. writing_extension: a related writing task

Return as JSON.
